description:
The wait is almost over for Vindication fans! Vindication Season 3 will release September 1st 2023!

Things go from bad to worse for Sergeant Travis and his friends and family now that Tomlinson is the Chief. Tre is assigned to investigate the murder discovered at the warehouse while Travis and Becky search desperately for answers.
